{"tid":2274625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國：「新疆東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動不再是恐怖組織」","createTime":"2020-11-06T14:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T07:06:30.000Z","uid":230104,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d218b87c2b50b80400fe2261a4ba304c9ba11f6","tid":2274625,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"美國政府宣布，不再把東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為恐怖組織。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院11月5日在聯邦公報（Federal Register）上發布的通知做如上表述。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧在通知中說，根據《移民和國籍法》(INA) 212(a)(B)(II)修訂條款的授權，撤銷東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動（Eastern Turkistan Islamic Movement）的&ldquo;恐怖組織&rdquo;的定列。<br />\n<br />\n維基百科說，美國等國是在2001年9月11日恐怖攻擊發生之後將東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動列為恐怖組織的。"},{"pid":"00e039c66eecfcf3f12e3c4ea435e22a3b19402c","tid":2274625,"uid":230104,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"對比起共產黨呢個真恐怖組織，東突厥只不過係為了自己民族不受侵吞"},{"pid":"05c9ee2b8311331c0ace05404e286cf9bfd1c5a5","tid":2274625,"uid":126889,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:20:19.000Z","msg":"連登: 我地唔係做恐怖分子"},{"pid":"d3f484ea80dbfb6244e00ea74c22a7c375f3b205","tid":2274625,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8f97491256a0e4979c697ec5ff60c718cb0092","tid":2274625,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"有條友沖出黎比人block 好低智"},{"pid":"62a6c87fdf901c154f320972d79ff3d41aaa38ea","tid":2274625,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"共鏟黨係有核武既恐怖分子"}]}